{"tid":2116111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家居隔離賓館衞生環境欠佳，環境不適合作隔離用途。 （無圖）","createTime":"2020-07-20T03:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T03:12:42.000Z","uid":240448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93fbb9587c81946791ad52d3fffeefc33c6be583","tid":2116111,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】疫情下，大部分抵港人士仍須接受十四日強制隔離，部分人選擇賓館作為家居隔離地點。本台發現有賓館衞生環境欠佳，業界承認部分賓館環境不適合作隔離用途。 <br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀的美麗都大廈幾乎每層都有賓館，<strong>有戴手帶的人等候入住，大廈有五間賓館，是勞工處建議外傭抵港後進行隔離。</strong><br />\n<br />\n本台去到這間建議名單的賓館，聲稱要訂房，賓館職員表示，會將須強制隔離的人士集中。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><em><strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"blue\">入到房間的窗戶未有緊閉，幾尺外就是其他的單位的窗口，天井到處都是垃圾煙蒂。拿開枕頭可以見到床單上有污迹，另一張床亦有，把被子張開，裏面有幾條頭髮，床下有煙蒂和液體。</span></span></strong></em></span><br />\n<br />\n賓館職員就指，房間有做清潔 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMZWdvC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMZWdvC.png&h=8d98b1b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iW8zKCi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiW8zKCi.png&h=3e18cf0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOTPyvF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOTPyvF.png&h=50ef2fac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmHXHo1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrmHXHo1.png&h=d93fd6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGDDrQH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGDDrQH.png&h=0c720298&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9yDrQJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9yDrQJ.png&h=e7f1c5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3hTDrQL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3hTDrQL.png&h=1b2f08b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvTTfKS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvTTfKS.png&h=3e68fede&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91383e7b9eefe9cdec33a2cc93f5c86527043513","tid":2116111,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8w3WXZg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8w3WXZg.png&h=d288143d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a1ad267b5a067f48118f6223f28de7be2a4b981","tid":2116111,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398615&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398615%26refer%3DShare&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=1baac551\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398615%26refer%3DShare&h=48eae457\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398615&amp;refer=Share</a>"}]}